## GET /api/orders/{id}

Scenario 19 (own order).

Request:
```json
GET /api/orders/20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer <jwt for Alice>
```

Response — 200 OK: same shape as the POST /api/orders 201 body above.

Response — 404 Not Found (ORD-013: a Customer can view only their own
orders — Bilal requesting Alice's order id gets 404, not 403, so the
order's existence isn't confirmed to someone who shouldn't see it):
```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "ORDER_NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "No order with this id."
  }
}
```

