## GET /api/orders

Scenarios 19 (own history) and 20 (admin, any customer).

Request (Alice, her own history):
```json
GET /api/orders
Authorization: Bearer <jwt for Alice>
```

Response — 200 OK:
```json
{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "20000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "status": "PLACED",
      "totalAmount": "308.98",
      "createdAt": "2026-07-13T14:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "total": 1
}
```

Request (Administrator, scenario 20 — support lookup for Chen):
```json
GET /api/orders?customerId=cccccccc-cccc-4ccc-8ccc-cccccccccccc
Authorization: Bearer <jwt for admin>
```

Response — 200 OK: same shape, Chen's orders. A Customer passing
`?customerId=` for anyone but themselves gets 403 (ORD-013).

