## Regression check against Phases 1–4

- Placing an order must call the real GetUser/GetProduct/ReserveStock
  gRPC methods — a Deactivated account (Phase 2) must be rejected here the
  same way it's rejected at login, and a Deactivated or nonexistent
  product (Phase 4) must be rejected the same way an out-of-stock one is.
- A product edited in Phase 4 after this order was placed must NOT change
  this order's stored `unitPrice`/`productName` — re-run Phase 4's PATCH
  on prod-0001 and re-fetch this order to confirm ORD-005 held.
